         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">22/6/95 ¶  ¶ Mainly I am writing to you this time, dear Mr Tepper, to ask whether freshly collected seeds (fruits) of  ¶ Atriplex nummularium ¶  are for sale in the seed merchants there and if so at w...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">95.06.22</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by Tepper: 'Reply 3.7.95'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>22/6/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hauptsächlich schreibe ich diesmal um vorzufragen, lieber Herr Tepper, ob in dortigen Samen-Handlungen frisch gesammelte Samen (Früchte) von <name key="Atriplex%20nummularium">Atriplex nummularium</name> käuflich sind, u wenn so- zu welchem Preise pr lb.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der grösste Theil der neuen erweiterten Ausgabe der "Select Plants" ist nun durch die Presse, so dass ich bald wieder in Stande sein werde die speciellen phytographischen Arbeiten wieder aufzunehmen, u so werde ich denn auch die rückständigen Benennungen verschiedener Sammlungen liefern können.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Falls Atriplex-Samen (Früchte) nicht dort kaufbar sind, möchte ich fragen, ob Sie jemand kennen in einer Region, wo <name key="Atriplex%20nummularium">Atriplex nummularium</name> (the Old Man Saltbush) vorkommt, der ein Angebot machen würde, zu welchem Preise er </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">wohl gereifte</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Früchte senden können mit gut entwickelte Samen pr lb.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie stets ehrend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Begrüssen Sie Dr Brown, u sagen Sie ihm, dass ich gern doch einmal im Leben selbst gesehen hätte.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">22/6/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mainly I am writing to you this time, dear Mr Tepper, to ask whether freshly collected seeds (fruits) of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Atriplex%20nummularium">Atriplex nummularium</name>
               </seg> are for sale in the seed merchants there and if so at what price per pound.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to O. Tepper, 9 April 1895<seg style=""> (in this edition as 95-04-09a)</seg>.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The largest part of the new enlarged edition of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select plants</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B95.08.04.</p>
               </note> is now through the press, so that I will soon be able to take up the special phytographic work again, and so I will then also be able to supply the overdue naming of various collections.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Atriplex</seg> seeds (fruits) are not for sale there, I would like to ask whether you know anyone in a region where <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Atriplex%20nummularium">Atriplex nummularium</name>
               </seg> (the Old Man Saltbush) occurs, who would make an offer at what price per pound he can send <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">well ripened</hi>
               </seg> fruits with well developed seeds.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Greetings to Dr Brown<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John Harris Browne. See M to O. Tepper, 12 November 1893, and M to O. Tepper, 27 January 1894 (<seg style="">in this edition as 94-01-27a)</seg>.</p>
               </note> and tell him that I would really like to have seen him once again in life.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Atriplex%20nummularium">Atriplex nummularium</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
